data.title: Champ's Glow
data.prompt: create a rap about winning a boxing championship v2
data.lyrics:
[Verse]
Came from the shadows, gloves laced, ready to fight
Eyes on the prize, gold belt shining in the light
Jab so quick, opponents hit the canvas fast
Roy Jones spirit, leaving legends in the past

[Chorus]
Champ's glow, shining, never gonna fade
Fists like thunder, every punch a renegade
Olympic dreams, I'm the king of the ring
Bow to the champ, hear the victory bells sing

[Verse 2]
Crowd's hyped up, feel the bass in the arena
Dodging every hook, moving slick like a dreamer
From the streets to the top, built my name with grit
Every round I dominate, never take a hit

[Bridge]
Gold in my veins, heart pumping like a drum
World champ status, watch the kingdom come
Roy Jones legacy, I'm carrying the flame
Undisputed warrior, forever in the game
